st celebrities serving their best looks and complimenting them are captivating hairstyles enough to turn heads. Like every year (and this time too) celebrities left no stones unturned when it came to serving us the glitz, the glam and the fashion to marvel at and enjoy.<br><br>With media coverage from all around the world wanting their own piece of the evening, a whole range of looks were caught on camera - from simple and minimalist to the more dramatic, below we go over some of our favourite hairstyles rocked by the very best on the red carpet this year at the 2021 Oscars.<br></span></p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-fHeRUh ixLxDV pf-26_"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-evcjhq leJfDA"><div class="sc-iJKOTD qriss pf-27_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-ctqQKy imxmpH pf-28_"><h2 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-bTfYFJ iRKxGS pf-29_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cbTzjv cciAhs pf-31_">
