urel hair contrasting against the boldness of her dress.&nbsp;</span></p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-fHeRUh ixLxDV pf-43_"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-evcjhq leJfDA"><div class="sc-iJKOTD qriss pf-44_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-ctqQKy imxmpH pf-45_"><h2 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-bTfYFJ iRKxGS pf-46_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cbTzjv cciAhs pf-48_">Margot Robbie’s Low Pony</span></h2></div></div></div><div class="sc-iJKOTD qriss pf-49_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-ctqQKy imxmpH pf-50_"><div data-pf-type="Custom.HTML" class="sc-kHOZwM gGGBsj pf-51_"><a id='9TIsiyfCQD1aum3y6Z0d8A' class='gie-slideshow' href='http://www.gettyimages.co.uk/detail/1314489746' target='_blank' style='color:#a7a7a7;text-decoration:none;font-weight:normal !important;border:none;display:inline-block;'>Embed from Getty Images</a><script>window.gie=window.gie||function(c){(gie.q=gie.q||[]).push(c)};gie(function(){gie.widgets.load({id:'9TIsiyfCQD1aum3y6Z0d8A',sig:'f2Dsz8PgvmK3F4EeT0KrtI4zASouhhdhM2qDgpoTxSk=',w:'594px',h:'396px',items:'1314489746,1314463109,1314456297',caption: true ,tld:'co.uk',is360: false })});</script><script src='//embed-cdn.gettyimages.com/widgets.js' charset='utf-8' async></script></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-fHeRUh ixLxDV pf-52_"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-evcjhq leJfDA"><div class="sc-iJKOTD qriss pf-53_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-ctqQKy imxmpH pf-54_"><p class="sc-uojGG ctGoIP pf-55_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cbTzjv cciAhs pf-57_">Margot Robbie also seemed a fan of effortless chic this year, gracing the carpet with her natural beauty as she appeared in sight in a shimmering floral black gown. She rocked freshly cut bangs that perfectly framed her face, keeping the rest of her luscious locks away from her face in a simple, low <b><a href="https://www.cliphair.co.uk/collections/clip-in-ponytail-extensions">ponytail</a></b> to detract from the dress. She completed the look with a classic black clutch in hand and statement pearl earrings.</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-iJKOTD qriss pf-58_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-ctqQKy imxmpH pf-59_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-bTfYFJ iRKxGS pf-60_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cbTzjv cciAhs pf-62_">Carey Mulligan’s Fierce Bun</span></h3></div></div></div><div class="sc-iJKOTD qriss pf-63_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-ctqQKy imxmpH pf-64_"><div data-pf-type="Custom.HTML" class="sc-kHOZwM gGGBsj pf-65_"><a id='rW_1uPMHRqhEuIcALB99bA' class='gie-slideshow' href='http://www.gettyimages.co.uk/detail/1314426041' target='_blank' style='color:#a7a7a7;text-decoration:none;font-weight:normal !important;border:none;display:inline-block;'>Embed from Getty Images</a><script>window.gie=window.gie||function(c){(gie.q=gie.q||[]).push(c)};gie(function(){gie.widgets.load({id:'rW_1uPMHRqhEuIcALB99bA',sig:'pFQWw9RYqRlPTAxM-t4XICoR6moSiy11DGJA6OrGeU4=',w:'419px',h:'594px',items:'1314426041,1314422589,1314422405',caption: true ,tld:'co.uk',is360: false })});</script><script src='//embed-cdn.gettyimages.com/widgets.js' charset='utf-8' async></script></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-fHeRUh ixLxDV pf-66_"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-evcjhq leJfDA"><div class="sc-iJKOTD qriss pf-67_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12